{
  "stem": "11671.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I mean, I took correspondence courses and Americanization classes and loved it, because I was studying all the time.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I just thought the food, and the clothing, and-- well, it took me a long time to adjust.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Like I wanted to wear bobby socks all the time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were going to this elegant party at the Palmer House in Chicago.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my mother-in-law-- my sister-in-law's best friend was getting married at the Palmer House in Chicago.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my mother-in-law said, you're not going with bobby socks.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I, and I said, well, this-- bobby socks, to me, were something very special.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because as children, we couldn't wear bobby socks because it was not-- we were too religious.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was too modern.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So when I came here, everything-- bobby socks, I would buy one in every color.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I was so proud I could wear.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So she-- we had this big argument.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't want to wear lipstick.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I had to learn every imaginable thing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I was determined to make this my happy place in life.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I took correspondence courses and learned how to type, and psychology course, and sewing-- beginners, intermediate, advanced-- and tailoring.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I took all these courses.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then my mother-in-law taught me Mahjong and Bridge and Kaluki.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, and I joined the bowling league.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I became pretty Americanized.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, I just took one class after another.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When we were in, in Italy, a group of people were passing through.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they said, did you know that your Mordechai, your brother, survived?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's when I found out, when we were in Italy.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After the war.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was, he was liberated from Dachau.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he was sent, you know, to hospital.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
